---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
import WorkTimeline from "@components/WorkTimeline.astro";
import GithubContributions from "@components/GithubContributions.astro";
import Link from "@components/Link.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import portrait from "@assets/about-me-1.jpg";
import { SITE, SOCIALS } from "@consts";
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn more about Regina Castro.">
  <Container>
    <aside data-pagefind-ignore>
      <section class="animate space-y-4 mt-10">
        <h1 class="font-semibold text-3xl" style="color: var(--primary-color);">About me</h1>
        <p>
I'm <i>Regina Castro</i>, a UX Designer based in Germany with 5+ years of experience, particularly in B2B SaaS and web experiences aimed at technical audiences.
For my next role, I'm looking to work on developer tools, AI-assisted interfaces, and accessibility-focused products.</p>
        <Image
            src={portrait}
            alt="Profile picture of Regina Castro"
            class="rounded-16"
          />
          <p>
            I'm currently working as a web and digital experience designer at <a href="https://www.beckman.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Beckman Coulter Life Sciences</a>, a global leader in life sciences and diagnostics, while pursuing my M.Sc. in Human-Computer Interaction at the University of Siegen. 
            Before that, I was a UX designer at <a href="https://www.questionpro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">QuestionPro</a>, a comprehensive survey and research software platform.
            </p>
            <p>
              On my free time, I love reading (specially magical realism and literary fiction), cooking and planning trips and concerts.
            My current personal goals are to ace the B2 German exam, learn creative coding and walk the Camino de Santiago. 
          </p>

          <hr class="my-12 border-gray-500" />

          <h2>My background</h2>
          <p>
          My journey started in graphic and motion design before evolving into UX design and research. Over time, my interest in how products actually work has led me toward design engineering and UI development.
          This blend of interests has allowed me to become comfortable across the entire product lifecycle, from research to design to UI implementation.
          </p>
          <hr class="my-12 border-gray-500" />
          <h2>What I'm looking for in my next role</h2>
          <p>
          I'm particularly interested in working on developer tools, AI-assisted interfaces, and accessibility-focused products that solve real user problems and have a positive impact on people's lives.
        </p>
          <h3>My pet peeves are:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Building features without strategy</li>
            <li>Thinking of accessibility as an afterthought</li>
            <li>Over-reliance on static mockups over interactive prototypes</li>
            <li>Prioritizing fancy visuals and animation over user needs and performance</li>
          </ul>
          <hr class="my-12 border-gray-500" />
          <h2>My strengths</h2>
          <div class="skills-cards grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="flex gap-3 not-prose group block overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-black/15 bg-white p-3 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-black/30 hover:shadow-sm focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-black/30 focus-visible:shadow-sm dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-neutral-900 dark:hover:border-white/40 dark:focus-visible:border-white/40">
              <div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">🧠 Research-backed design</h3>
                <p>I bring formal UX research methodologies to my design process and validate my ideas with real user feedback.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 not-prose group block overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-black/15 bg-white p-3 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-black/30 hover:shadow-sm focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-black/30 focus-visible:shadow-sm dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-neutral-900 dark:hover:border-white/40 dark:focus-visible:border-white/40">
              <div><h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">🧩 Systems-thinking</h3>
                <p>I know how damaging technical debt can be, so I emphasize designing for scalable systems and reusable components.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 not-prose group block overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-black/15 bg-white p-3 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-black/30 hover:shadow-sm focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-black/30 focus-visible:shadow-sm dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-neutral-900 dark:hover:border-white/40 dark:focus-visible:border-white/40">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">💻 Technical depth</h3>
                <p>
                  I can build components and prototypes using HTML, CSS, and Tailwind, and I leverage AI-assisted coding tools to accelerate my workflow responsibly.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 not-prose group block overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-black/15 bg-white p-3 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-black/30 hover:shadow-sm focus-visible:-translate-y-0.5 focus-visible:border-black/30 focus-visible:shadow-sm dark:border-white/20 dark:bg-neutral-900 dark:hover:border-white/40 dark:focus-visible:border-white/40">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">🤝 Collaboration</h3>
                <p>
                  I enjoy collaborating closely with developers and have experience using version control tools like GitHub to stay aligned.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
         
      <section class="animate space-y-6 mt-12">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-y-2">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">My journey so far</h2>
        </div>
        <WorkTimeline />
      </section>
      <section class="animate space-y-4 mt-12">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Let's Connect</h2>
        <article>
          <p>
            If you want to get in touch with me about something or just to say
            hi, reach out on social media or send me an email.
          </p>
        </article>
        <ul class="not-prose flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {
            SOCIALS.map((SOCIAL) => (
              <li class="flex gap-x-2 text-nowrap">
                <Link
                  href={SOCIAL.HREF}
                  external
                  aria-label={`${SITE.TITLE} on ${SOCIAL.NAME}`}
                >
                  {SOCIAL.NAME}
                </Link>
                {"/"}
              </li>
            ))
          }
          <li class="line-clamp-1">
            <Link
              href={`mailto:${SITE.EMAIL}`}
              aria-label={`Email ${SITE.TITLE}`}
            >
              {SITE.EMAIL}
            </Link>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </aside>
  </Container>
</Layout>
